MappingData.Description: This mapping provides a 1-N relationship between a ISO3 code entity (identifying a country) and one or more MarineRegions id (identifying an Exclusive Economic Zone - EEZ), giving the sovereignty of country over EEZs. The mapping is entirely constructed from the VLIZ Marine Regions MarBound database.
